node.text:
Our friends over at @Classicdadmoves helped us celebrate the ultimate golf dad with all the Chili’s food and some ice cold @michelobultra - just in time for Father’s Day! 

Keep an eye out - we might just have an epic Father’s Day giveaway coming your way!

node.text: Now, when you grab a dad-sized bite at Chili’s, you’re doing it for a great cause. How? We partnered with @classicdadmoves & kids @stjude to help raise awareness (and money, too). Head to your local Chili’s today and #CreateAPepper But first, check out our IG story to see the kids imitate their dads.

👉👉 Enter to win at link in bio 🌶

node.text: Summer is in full swing, and we’ve got just the ice-cold ‘Rita you need to keep your chill. Stay tuned for our announcement of August’s $5 Marg of the Month!

node.text: There is nothing wrong with being an adult and ordering chicken crispers every time you go to Chili’s.

node.text: Pour up a celebration on #NationalTequilaDay with with $5 Frose and Captain’s Stay-Cay ‘Ritas, $6 Presidente Margaritas, or take the refresh-tivities anywhere with a $30 Margarita Gallon Bag. Party at our place or get them To-Go all day long on 7/24!

National Tequila Day is tomorrow and we want to share the love from our media and influencer event last night. Tag your best marg drinking buddy below for a chance to snag one of our National Tequila Day goodie bags! Share to your story for an extra chance to win - good luck! 

Check out the rules in bio!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Chili's Grill & Bar on July 19, 2021. May be an image of drink.

node.text: July’s $5 Margarita of the Month is none other than our Captain’s Stay-Cay ‘Rita! This top-shelf mix is sure to take your taste buds on a refreshing trip with every sip.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Chili's Grill & Bar on July 17, 2021.

node.text:
Chili’s favorites are so good they belong on more than just your table. Drop a comment below with 🙏 for a chance to win your own Chili’s temporary tattoo for #NationalTattooDay 🌶

Check out rules in bio

node.text: That 50% discount has us like ( ͡👁 ͜ʖ ͡👁). Apply today at the link in our bio!

node.text: The Dog days of Summer are here ☀️☀️☀️

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Chili's Grill & Bar on July 12, 2021. May be an image of drink.

node.text: Name that Captain! Check the clues in the picture and tell us what Captain comes to mind in the comments below—then BECOME the Captain with our $5 Captain’s Stay-Cay ‘Rita. The clock is ticking, so make sure to try this ‘Rita before it sets sail at the end of the month!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Chili's Grill & Bar on July 10, 2021. May be an image of text.

node.text: Your get together is always good To-Go when there’s Chili’s involved. No matter if you’re chilling by the pool or just chilling in general, we’ve got the Margs (and everything else) ready to tag along wherever your weekend takes you!
